     <narrative xml:lang="EN">WSH-I4: Number of people having access to sufficient and safe water for domestic use</narrative>
    </title>
    <description>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#x2022; Water supply to 6000 individuals (1000HH) through two-month water trucking using a voucher system.
&#x2022; Chlorination of water and monitor water quality and quantity.
&#x2022; Rehabilitation/upgrading of 3 existing boreholes for 15000 individuals (2500HH) through hybrid solar system.
&#x2022; Procure and install 30 water storage bladders (9.000 ltr/unit).
&#x2022; Train 3 water management committtees ( each comprising 7 members) where atleast 50% are female
&#x2022; Establish an appropriate and affordable water collection fees in collabration with community leadership 
